<HEADLINE> Debbie Matenopoulos To Write Book </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Debbie Matenopoulos, nudged from her slot on  
ABC's ``The View,'' apparently learned enough from the experience 
to write an inspirational book. 
</P>
<P>
	The 24-year-old, who gabbed with the likes of Barbara Walters,  
Joy Behar, Star Jones and Meredith Vieira on the show, has been 
replaced with Channel One's Lisa Ling. 
</P>
<P>
